  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Empower A Student In Ghana Through Education</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project addresses the lack of access to education for Ghanaian youth. As a result of costly tuition and extreme poverty, children are forced to help provide for their families instead of study. Our primary goal is to support young scholars affected by these socio-economic burdens. By funding and creating scholarships, mentorships, tutoring and capacity building opportunities, we aim to empower students to become future leaders in their community in the region of Accra, Ghana.</narrative>
  </description>
